Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.85,0:00:05.16,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just as flowing water has no form, and the breeze is invisible
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.16,0:00:07.63,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Deductions take all shapes and styles in each and every case to be solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:09.23,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today, we must all change out way of thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:10.96,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What should be on, isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.96,0:00:12.50,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees through to the one & only truth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.50,0:00:13.37,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A child in appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.37,0:00:14.37,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}With the I.Q. of an adult
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.37,0:00:16.70,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No case is left unsolved with Detective Conan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:46.52,Title,Sign,0,0,0,,A MYSTERIOUS GUNSHOT\NECHO IN THE DARKNESS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:51.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So many handsome actors star in those Monday night mystery shows...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:55.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited, I wonder what kind of stories we'll get to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.69,0:01:56.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.79,0:01:59.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just because our client's the president of some company produces movies,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This kid insisted on tagging along...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.63,0:02:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I already told you but my job is to protect the client's mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:10.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:15.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she was injured when she was attacked 3 days ago, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.31,0:02:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is being the president of a finance company such a dangerous job?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:21.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I've heard she can be pretty vicious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.19,0:02:25.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that means she's got a lot of enemies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:26.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess you could say that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:31.09,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:34.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Kogoro Mouri,\NI'm a private investigator...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.23,0:02:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a 7'o clock appointment to see Ms. Etsuko Furukawa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:43.14,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes, you're expected. I'll unlock the gate now. Please come in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:46.08,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:55.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan? We're going
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:57.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, OK!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:02:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please have some coffee...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:05.83,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry about this,\NMs. Furukawa is usually punctual...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:05.83,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Azusa Machida (22)\NFurukawa Family Maid
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.43,0:03:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, don't be bothered
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:13.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's alright with you, while we're waiting,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:15.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could we watch the television?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:19.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. That TV's been on the brink since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:21.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing shows on the screen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:23.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:27.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot, you have some nerve asking like that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.32,0:03:28.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:29.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me Miss,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:31.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the window on the far left on the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,2nd floor facing the street was open...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:36.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That room belongs to the owner of this place
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:39.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Katsue Furukawa, president of the Furukawa Finance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pardon me for asking, but who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:44.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kohji Furukawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm her son
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.07,0:03:51.07,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That window is always open at this time of day to air out the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:51.14,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Kohji Furukawa (22)\NEldest Son Unemployed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:53.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Azusa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.64,0:03:54.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:04:00.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're that detective my sister hired, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I pity you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's just going to use you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:06.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Use me? You say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:10.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that's her now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:12.36,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:14.46,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's me, Etsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:16.97,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Etsuko Furukawa (40)\NEldest Daughter TV Producer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:16.93,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm late. Hurry & let me in
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.93,0:04:18.53,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes, right away
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:24.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mouri, I'm terribly sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:27.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had some last minute businesss to take care of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kohji...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hi sis, long time no see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:34.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't mom ban you from this house the last time you were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:41.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aw shut up, this is MY house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:44.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And by the way, what's with that watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.06,0:04:44.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:48.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said digitals were cheap stuff and you wouldn't be caught dead with one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:51.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You had to pawn that Swiss watch you were so proud of to pay for your debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:58.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:00.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Kohji
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:03.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll bet you're here to get mom to pay off your debts again, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:04.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:07.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what about you sis, hiring a private detective to butter mom up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:08.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so obvious
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:12.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Things seem pretty messy around here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:13.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:17.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss Etsuko's company is on the verge of bankruptcy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it seems Mr. Kohji has a lot of gambling debts
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:22.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And some mobsters after him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But their mother Katsue has a lot of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:29.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, Mrs. Furukawa never lends money to those
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She feels cannot repay her, regardless if they're her children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:35.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the past though, she did lend Kohji
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:38.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A lot of money but it got out of and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So she finally banned him from the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:42.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Azusa, what is wrong with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:43.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:45.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you telling them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:46.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:48.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's alseep in her room, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:49.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:51.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Azusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:54.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead of doing everything my sister tells you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should go out with me sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.07,0:06:01.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I ask, I can get mom to forget about all the money you owe her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:05.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kohji! If you have nothing better to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:07.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go out and buy something to give mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:09.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Azusa
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.61,0:06:10.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:15.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, about Azusa's debts...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:22.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, I heard she made a stain on mom's Persian rug today
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:25.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just for that, she's not getting a bonus this year
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:29.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since that wasn't enough, mom made her write an IOU for the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:31.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's happened several times before,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:34.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of these days, I'm sure she's going to blow up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:39.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh well, I guess I'll go and buy mom a little something...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just hate taking sis's advice though...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:45.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's with this family...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:48.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:52.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother, wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She usually gets up right away
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:06:59.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's locked...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:03.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she took some of the sleeping pills the doctor prescribed and fell asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:05.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's still so early...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.67,0:07:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it certainly is hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:09.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:10.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sweating...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:13.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:19.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:24.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:26.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother, open this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:29.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:32.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mouri, something's wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:34.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It came from mom's room...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:35.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear a weird sound from mom's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:42.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard a gunshot in mom's room!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:48.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's locked. Do you have a spare key?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.64,0:07:53.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The key was a special order item and mom has the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.15,0:07:57.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no other choice, we've got to break the door down
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:57.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:07:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:02.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:03.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.26,0:08:05.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so dark you can't see a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:12.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's the light swtich?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.64,0:08:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the wall to your left...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:22.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:23.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:25.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mustn't go in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:30.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a murder! We have to preserve the crime scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.89,0:08:35.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:36.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, call the police
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:37.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:45.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She's been shot in the forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:47.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She died instantaneously...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:50.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There're no signs of a struggle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:51.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:53.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Footprints lead to the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:58.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The killer must've used that ladder...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:02.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But the position of the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:11.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why you! How many times do\NI have to repeat myself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.06,0:09:12.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.73,0:09:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:21.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on and get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:21.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ouch, ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:25.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim is Katsue Furukawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,64 years old, president of a finance company
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:34.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The footprints around the body match those we found around the ladder outside
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:36.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim was attacked just\N3 days earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.06,0:09:41.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was the same assailant...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:42.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh officer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:43.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone you didn't know came in through the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:48.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you run for the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:50.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You little brat!\NI told you to stay out of this!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:52.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, Conan's right
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:53.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:56.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the body was near the window
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:10:01.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can assume the victim noticed the intruder and approached the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:06.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means the intruder was probably someone the victim knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:12.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's question everyone who was in the house when the murder occurred
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:12.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes sir
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:16.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About when you discovered the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:20.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ms. Etsuko Furukawa and\NMs. Azusa Machida, you two
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:22.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,went to the victim's room on the 2nd floor to wake her up
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:24.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And heard the gunshot...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:27.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Mr. Mouri and Mr. Kohji Furukawa
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:30.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Broke the door down and then discovered the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:32.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I correct so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:35.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:39.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you heard the gunshot, did you notice anything out of the ordinary?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm very certain it was when\NMiss Etsuko bent down
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:46.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To pick up the handkerchief she dropped, that's when we heard the gunshot...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:48.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about after the gunshot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:50.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.69,0:10:52.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, just a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:54.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long are you going to keep us here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:58.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's obvious she was killed by the same person who attacked her 3 days ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:01.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Put out an all points bulletin, do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's already been taken care of. However,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:07.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judging from the position of the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:10.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a good chance she knew her killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She knew the killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are we suspects?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I left this morning and haven't been in mom's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:20.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:28.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm, thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:29.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Azusa Machida...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:30.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:35.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems the victim treated you quite badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:41.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to your neighbor, you were complaining about it this evening
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:44.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said, "I'll get back at her for this!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:47.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:49.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Azusa, you didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh-oh, you finally lost your temper, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:56.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, you're wrong. I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:58.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true, I did say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:12:00.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but let me explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I spilled some tea in the madam's room this evening...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.27,0:12:10.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wiped everything that got wet
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:14.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The clock, the remote control for the television, even the rug!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:18.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But madam insisted I stained the rug
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she said she wasn't going to give me a bonus this year
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:24.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then on top of that, she made me write an IOU...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's why I said what I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.42,0:12:31.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But like I said before, when the gunshot went off,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.39,0:12:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was outside the door with Ms. Etsuko
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:37.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:41.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means you two have an alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:44.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Mr. Furukawa, where were you then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:45.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:47.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a good question, Kohji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:52.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As soon as your sister and Azusa went upstairs, you left the living room
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:56.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the gunshot, you took some time before joining us upstairs didn't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:57.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ho, hold on just one minute
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:12:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't kill her
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:00.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:03.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I was going to go buy mom a gift...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And just as I was going out the gate,\NI heard a strange sound so I rushed back
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:11.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means you have no alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.24,0:13:17.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't we just talk about this a little more
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:20.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The way things stand now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:23.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Kohji does seem the most suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:25.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But something just doesn't seem right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:31.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey, there you are kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:34.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you here to help that famous detective again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:35.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sort of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He told me to ask you if there was a cassette radio
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:40.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or something with a timer in the room
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:41.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haha...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:45.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it, if you set the timer, you can pre-set the gunshot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:47.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, we didn't find anything like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The TV's an old model and it doesn't have a timer either...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:53.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I was wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:55.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mr. Tome
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:56.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:58.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good hunting, little detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:01.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I was so sure there was a trick behind to that gunshot...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:03.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A blue-white light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.75,0:14:07.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What nonsense are you talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:09.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just before the gunshot, I happened to look up at mom's room
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:15.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And her room was lit up with a blue-white light but it got dark right after that again
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:17.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got to believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:19.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A blue-white light...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:22.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But Mr. Tome just told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:25.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's going on here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:26.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:27.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You can do it that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:29.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's why that thing was there
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:31.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:33.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:35.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:38.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:44.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're smart to pick up on that kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.06,0:14:46.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That struck me as strange too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:48.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Now I've got all the evidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:50.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That person is the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:14:57.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:15:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good grief, where's this solid proof you were talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ulp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:07.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:09.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's happening again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:12.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm counting on you, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:14.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it true, you know who the killer is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:18.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Mouri...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.49,0:15:20.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the?! Oh, I know that look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:24.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes Inspector Megure,\NI've figured everything out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:27.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have everyone come here to this room please
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:28.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So everyone's present?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:36.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First of all Inspector Megure, judging from the position of the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.07,0:15:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've deducted the victim knew the killer, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.94,0:15:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:45.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when we broke the door down and entered the room, the lights were all off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:51.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Then how did the victim see the killer's face...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:53.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:54.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:16:00.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Furukawa was killed earlier in the day, while there was still sunlight!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.43,0:16:06.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B, but what about the gunshot we all heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:12.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That gunshot was staged by the killer to be used as an alibi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer took the remote control for the television
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:18.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And switched it on later to play the television
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.05,0:16:21.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Mouri,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:24.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that mean the killer had to have prior knowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:27.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of the exact time the gunshot would be heard on television?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:31.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:34.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, there's only one person here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who would know the exact time
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:41.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A gunshot would be heard on the television...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:48.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The gunshot was heard at about 7:30.\N7:29 and 32 seconds to be exact
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:54.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the exact time a gun is shot in a show\NMs. Furukawa's company produces
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:59.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ms. Etsuko Furukawa, you are the murderer!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:05.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The crime probably took place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:06.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the evening,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:10.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ms. Furukawa climbed in through the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:13.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her mother sees her and goes to the window
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:17.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And is shot by a gun with a silencer
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ms. Furukawa then changed her clothes and came to meet with us
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:26.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Acting as if nothing had happened
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.85,0:17:30.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then calculating the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:33.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She took Azusa, who would act as her witness,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:36.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Upstairs and deliberately dropped her handkerchief
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:40.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then pretends to pick it up as she presses the remote control button!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:45.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did I made any mistakes anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:47.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the blue-white light Kohji was talking about was from the television...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:56.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If even a second was off from the timing of switching the remote control on,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:18:00.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Other noises would have been heard and the trick wouldn't have worked
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:05.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you wore a digital watch today, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:09.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it was also you who broke the TV in living room, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:12.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the gunshot was heard upstairs, it would've been suspicious
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:15.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the same sound came from the television downstairs, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:18.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Can you prove any of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any proof I did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:21.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.57,0:18:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the body was found, you pretended to cry and crouched down
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:30.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When no one was looking, you took the remote control out. Then slid it on the rug
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:33.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And returned it under the table, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:36.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you put a little too much strength into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:39.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it was supposed to look like it fell from the table
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it slid under the legs instead
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.49,0:18:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your fingerprints were on that remote control
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:49.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course they would be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I go in and out of this room practically every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But earlier you said you left the room this morning and never returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.94,0:19:04.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was talking about today. But I was in here yesterday and the day before too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:05.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh really...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:07.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Azusa
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:08.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you do with the remote control when you spilled the tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:17.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, the tea spilled on it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:19.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I wiped it clean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:20.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:22.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet you forgot to wipe it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.77,0:19:27.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did not! I wiped it absolutely clean!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.30,0:19:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh brother, this argument is getting us nowhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:36.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tome! Please explain to everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:38.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:42.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:43.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anytime
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:45.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ahem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.19,0:19:51.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found two sets of fingerprints on the remote control found on the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:54.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One! The left hand print of Ms. Etsuko Furukawa
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:56.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Including the thumb to baby finger and palm print
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:59.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Second! The left hand print of Ms. Azusa Machida
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:01.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Including the thumb to baby finger and palm print
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:03.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, what did I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}your{\i0} prints are on it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:08.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that all, Mr. Tome?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:12.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:14.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then that settles it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:17.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:20.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Azusa didn't forget to wipe the remote control
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:22.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:24.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something was missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:26.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she had forgotten to wipe the remote control,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,something else had to be on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:31.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Katsue Furukawa's fingerprints, it was her room
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:33.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,& since she's always handling the remote control,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:36.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,her prints should have been on it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:50.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was all her fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:54.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...She knew\NI was having financial problems
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:20:58.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but she wouldn't lend me a single cent...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.53,0:21:02.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet she'd pay off all of Kohji's gambling debts...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.83,0:21:04.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was always that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:07.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was always Kohji this, Kohji that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:10.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she pampered him because she gave birth to him in her later years...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:12.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kohji was everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:14.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.44,0:21:15.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss Furukawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:18.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not that\NI don't understand how you feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.48,0:21:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do, but
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:22.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...think about it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.72,0:21:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've just committed a murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.62,0:21:27.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've killed your own mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:33.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...I want you to think deeply about what you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.09,0:23:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There, that should do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.19,0:23:14.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It works!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.83,0:23:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.60,0:23:18.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aw, it was nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.33,0:23:21.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He may not look it but Mr. Takagi's a video freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.30,0:23:25.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's goes to rent videos every night, he's addicted,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.58,0:23:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gunshots?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.08,0:23:37.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got a case to solve...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.29,0:23:42.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Somebody tell him it's already over!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.63,0:23:49.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You've...\NYou've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.37,0:23:52.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to bathe with Conan, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.68,0:23:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something's come over Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.41,0:23:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she suspects who I really am?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.15,0:24:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.46,0:24:15.40,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,PERILOUS RETURN\NDETECTIVES IN THE CAVE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.33,0:24:18.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.33,0:24:20.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Misfire
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:22.71,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The next episode is finally the special series!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.71,0:24:24.71,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,If you watch all of it, you'll be able to meet that person!
